room_title: Escape room "A Day in the Life" by Panic Escape Room in Chicago
room_address: 990 Grand Canyon Pkwy Hoffman Estates, IL 60169
room_description:
Anya decided to take a break from her "Great Responasbilites" to try to focus on her Art......but is struggling with artist block!

She visits a local shop for motivation but gets more than she bargained for..... Will you step up to the "Mantle" and help her!?  Her fate may rest in your hands!
